1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>略。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>别忘了小数怎么搞。</li>\n<li><strong>舍入(rounding)</strong> 的问题。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-07266b5fc04bf44a\" style=\"position: relative;\">3. 编码 Coding<a href=\"#anchor-07266b5fc04bf44a\" aria-label=\"anchor 07266b5fc04bf44a permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-cae25943b71e3f57\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.1. 独热码 &#x26; 独冷码<a href=\"#anchor-cae25943b71e3f57\" aria-label=\"anchor cae25943b71e3f57 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>独热码(one-hot)</strong>  要求比特向量中只有一位是  <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>，例如  <code class=\"language-text\">0001</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">0010</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">0100</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">1000</code>  等；对应的还有<strong>独冷码(one-cold)</strong>。</p>\n<p>使用这种编码的好处是，决定或改变状态机目前的状态的成本相对较低，容易设计也容易检测非法行为等。</p>\n<p>但是相对应的，缺点是信息表示率较低，非法状态非常多而有效状态很少。</p>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-f557f689bafab6cd\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.2. BCD 码 Binary Coded Decimal Code<a href=\"#anchor-f557f689bafab6cd\" aria-label=\"anchor f557f689bafab6cd permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-548e9a0a72aeac76\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.2.1. 8421 码 8421 Code<a href=\"#anchor-548e9a0a72aeac76\" aria-label=\"anchor 548e9a0a72aeac76 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>最经典的 BCD 码是 8421 码，用 4 位二进制表示一个<strong>十进制</strong>位，weight 分别为 8421，所以 BCD 码也叫做 8421 码。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BCD 码在做加法时，类比十进制加法一样按 4 位一组计算。</li>\n<li>当两位相加的结果大于 10 时需要做一个 +6 的修正。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/02/29/WFiHh2bR.png\"alt=\"\" style=\"width: 320px; \" ></p>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-6edc30c40c6ca2ef\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.2.2. 余三码 Excess3 Code<a href=\"#anchor-6edc30c40c6ca2ef\" aria-label=\"anchor 6edc30c40c6ca2ef permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p><strong>余三码(Excess3)</strong> 是 BCD 码的一个改进，其核心思路是在 BCD 码的基础上，<strong>增加一个大小为 3 的偏移量</strong>。（每一位都是先 +3 再转化成二进制）</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>进位检测</strong>：注意到 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>=</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mrow><mn>16</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">3=\\dfrac{16-10}{2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0074em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">16</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">10</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span></span>，这样十进制下能进位的两个数位，在余三码下也刚好能进位。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"anchor-640fd36540111dad\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.2.3. 2421 码 2421 Code<a href=\"#anchor-640fd36540111dad\" aria-label=\"anchor 640fd36540111dad permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<p>2421 码与 8421 码类似，但是每一位的权值分别为 2421。<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>∼</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0\\sim 9</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∼</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span></span></span> 中的每一个数都对应一个唯一的 2421 码，但将不在这一对应表中的二进制编码转换回十进制时也能对应到 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn><mo>∼</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0\\sim 9</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∼</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span></span></span> 中的数字。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>2421 码的一个特性是 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">9-x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">9</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> 的 2421 码互补，其中 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>∼</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=0 \\sim 4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∼</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span></span></span></span></span> 时的 2421 码就是其二进制，而 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>∼</mo><mn>9</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x=5\\sim 9</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">5</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">∼</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span></span></span> 的 2421 码就是 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">9-x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">9</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> 与 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>111</mn><msub><mn>1</mn><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1111_{(2)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9996em;vertical-align:-0.3552em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">111</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3448em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5198em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mopen mtight\">(</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span><span class=\"mclose mtight\">)</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3552em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 异或后的结果。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-1f85f60801c0a436\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.3. 格雷码 Gray Code<a href=\"#anchor-1f85f60801c0a436\" aria-label=\"anchor 1f85f60801c0a436 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>格雷码(gray code)</strong> 是一种<strong>可靠性编码(reliable code)</strong>。相邻的两个数字的格雷码只有一个 bit 上的 0/1 不同。</p>\n<p><details open disabled class=\"callout callout-type-info\"><summary> 可靠性编码</summary><div class=\"callout-content\"><p>\nReliable codes are codes that can reduce error, detect error and correct error are called reliable code.</p></div></details></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/03/07/stANosFs.png\"alt=\"从光学透镜的角度理解格雷码\" style=\"width: 200px; \" ><span class=\"image-alt\">从光学透镜的角度理解格雷码</span></p>\n<p><details open disabled class=\"callout callout-type-important\"><summary> 二进制反射格雷码(Binary Reflected Gray Code, BRGC)</summary><div class=\"callout-content\"><p></p><p>数字 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span> 对应的格雷码为：\n<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mtext> XOR </mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mtext> SHR </mtext><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x \\text{ XOR } (x \\text{ SHR } 1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\"> XOR </span></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\"> SHR </span></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p></div></details></p>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-64e756f843dce169\" style=\"position: relative;\">3.4. 奇偶校验码 Parity Code<a href=\"#anchor-64e756f843dce169\" aria-label=\"anchor 64e756f843dce169 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>奇偶校验码(parity code)</strong> 也是一种可靠性编码，分为偶校验码和奇校验码两种。<strong>偶校验码(even parity code)</strong> 保证数据中为 1 的 bit 数为偶数，<strong>奇校验码(odd parity code)</strong> 保证为奇数。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/03/07/ffltccLq.png\"alt=\"奇偶校验码示例\" style=\"width: 400px; \" ><span class=\"image-alt\">奇偶校验码示例</span></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-4090c85699954230\">1. 数字系统 Digital Systems</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-8f5440fe0c63395c\">1.1. 信息表达 Information Representation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-774eb4c4cc23ba6e\">1.2. 逻辑系统 Logic System</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-b50d31f2b4ff1953\">1.3. 数字计算机 Digital Computer</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-7beebcc9099db58a\">2. 数字系统 Number System</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-7db335e9a95e5895\">2.1. 进制 Base</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-83dd4394c6fe5d4b\">2.2. 进制转换</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-07266b5fc04bf44a\">3. 编码 Coding</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-cae25943b71e3f57\">3.1. 独热码 &#x26; 独冷码</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-f557f689bafab6cd\">3.2. BCD 码 Binary Coded Decimal Code</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-1f85f60801c0a436\">3.3. 格雷码 Gray Code</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-64e756f843dce169\">3.4. 奇偶校验码 Parity Code</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Ch1 Digital Systems and Information","date":null,"description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/course/dd/note/1/","isDoc":true,"category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"18032122-3ba7-5f89-9a2f-896fbea22a7d","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":"[{\"slug\":\"/course/dd\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/dd/index.md\",\"title\":\"Intro\"},{\"title\":\"Notes\",\"children\":[{\"slug\":\"/course/dd/note/1\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/dd/note/1.md\",\"title\":\"Ch1 Digital Systems and Information\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/dd/note/2\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/dd/note/2.md\",\"title\":\"Ch2 Combinational Logic Circuits\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/dd/note/3\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-